{"tid":1220783,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"童謠抗暴…入黎將呢條youtube 片推上熱門","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T15:32:09.000Z","uid":59570,"like":173,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7bfad451bd1eeb4bf536401b20dfa33673e73e23","tid":1220783,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請廣傳並幫刷view 上熱門比多d人聽，<br />\n<br />\n入去睇一次，睇完再share 片比朋友睇一次，得廿零秒刷view 好容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少呢d兒歌，一影響就影響幾代既小朋友，雨傘改過幾多歌今日大家仲會唱仲記得？。但今時今日既小朋友仲唱緊十幾年前既聖誕老人剝衫剝褲&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n呢d兒歌先係最易流傳既記憶!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要將盲幫政府既黑警既社會地位變成過街老鼠，四面楚歌<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lciq_hERcGY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Flciq_hERcGY&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=e715fc54\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lciq_hERcGY</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最好推到黑警d仔女睇完父親節唱比佢地爸爸媽媽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a5279748825e4803bf975f8fa8ef0c89053e28","tid":1220783,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4118fe40759f451aa29c15bee918be21e9448108","tid":1220783,"uid":63770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"呼籲 616 一齊抄警犬牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1220570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1220570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44e9a09317e4fb330e66fe2c34998fecb34540dd","tid":1220783,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime